data.title: New Zealand Football / Soccer Clubs Ranking
data.meta_description: Auckland City is the best football / soccer team in New Zealand today. Team Wellington are the second best. The third place belongs to Waitakere United, while Eastern Suburbs and Canterbury United complete the Top 5 from the national ranking. Check out our complete club world, continental and national rankings.
data.text:
Did you know...

Sir Alex Ferguson became the first manager to lead a foreign club to the final of the FIFA Club World Cup as Manchester United became world champions during the 2008 edition.
